OL,4,G2000FRace Across the World: The Final
OL,5,     GAfter more than 11,000km across
OL,6,     Geight countries, the teams face
OL,7,     Gone final test of endurance as
OL,8,     Gthey race to claim victory at the
OL,9,     Gfinish line in Hatgal, Mongolia.
OL,10,G2100FRace Across the World
OL,11,     GSix months after the race, all
OL,12,     Gfive teams reunite to relive
OL,13,     Gtheir 12,000km journey from
OL,14,     GPalermo to Mongolia, with unseen
OL,15,     Gmoments and unprecedented behind-
OL,16,     Gthe-scenes access.
